name: Amazon ElastiCache
description: Amazon ElastiCache is a managed in-memory data store and cache service offered by Amazon Web Services (AWS).  It acts as a high-speed layer between your application and database, storing frequently accessed data in memory for quicker retrieval.

name: Amazon Keyspaces
description: Amazon Keyspaces is a managed Apache Cassandra-compatible database service offered by Amazon Web Services (AWS).

name: Amazon RDS
description: Amazon Relational Database Service (RDS) is a managed database service offered by Amazon Web Services (AWS).
